casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Dever, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Dever (1995), 73 Ohio St.3d 722.]

(No. 95-831 Submitted July 26, 1995 Decided October 11, 1995.) *723Joseph T. Deters, Hamilton County Prosecuting Attorney, and Christian J. Schaefer, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. Frederick M. Dever, Jr., pro se. Per Curiam.

We affirm the decision of the court of appeals for the reasons stated in its opinion.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
